Drop dead gorgeous, perfectly figure with finely toned  figure. Her green eyes, dark brown skin, and perfect raven hair, only adds to her exotic looks.  There is a strange tattoo on the small of her back...two red eyes over a ranseur surrounded by a barbed tail with it seems to be covered a bit by a flame...See DM on Lore Check
Beautiful figured and well toned, their devilish tails, red skin and pitch black eyes mark her as a child of the lower planes.

Woven to be versatile whether for pleasure or for the ease of movement of combat.  The buckle on the front of an interesting design a pair of glowing red eyes above a horizontal ransuer, both encircled by a barbed red tail.
Woven and enchanted to inflict great amounts of pain whether it be in combat or a simple touch if the wearer wills it.
